-- Luxembourg has launched investigation into Espirito Santo holdings
-- 
-- Fri Jun 27, 2014 09:23AM EDT
-- None



BRUSSELS, June 27 (Reuters) - Luxembourg justice authorities have launched an investigation into three holding companies of Portugal's Banco Espirito Santo <BES.LS> over alleged breaches of company law, a spokesman said on Friday.

The spokesman said the investigation against Espírito Santo International SA, Espirito Santo Control SA and Espírito Santo Financial Group SA was launched on May 22.